                    <h3>Amazon Rainforest</h3>
                    <p>Spans <span class="highlight">5.5 million square kilometers</span> across South America.</p>
                    <p>Stretches across <span class="highlight">9 countries</span>, with 60% in Brazil.</p>
                    <p>Home to approximately <span class="highlight">10% of all species on Earth</span>.</p>
