                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="icon">ü¶Å</div>
                    <h3>African Savanna</h3>
                    <p>Covers approximately <span class="highlight">13 million square kilometers</span>.</p>
                    <p>Home to the "Big Five": lions, leopards, elephants, buffalo, and rhinos.</p>
                    <p>Serengeti's Great Migration involves <span class="highlight">1.5 million wildebeest</span> and
